    <section id="sect-00002">
    <title>bool data type</title>
    <para id="para-00002">People often ask true/false questions or binary questions. Ex: True or False: I like pineapple on pizza. The response is a boolean value, meaning the value is either true or false. The <term id="term-00001">bool</term> data type, standing for boolean, represents a binary value of either True or False. <code class="python inline-code">True</code> and <code class="python inline-code">False</code> are keywords, and capitalization <span class="purple-code">is required</span>.</para>
